title: FM Azerbaijan arrives on two-day visit
content:
ISLAMABAD, May 29 (APP): Foreign Minister of Azerbaijan Jeyhun Bayramov on Wednesday arrived here on a two-day official visit.
At the Islamabad International Airport, he was warmly received by Additional Foreign Secretary (Afghanistan and West Asia) Ahmed Naseem Warraich, Ministry of Foreign Affairs posted on X account.
Foreign Minister Jeyhun Bayramov will call on Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif and hold extensive discussions with Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar.
